# Creating a personal website

## Difficulty
Beginner

## Project's Author
* [Antonio Valero]( Antonio Valero Barbero | LinkedIn)

## Objectives
Develop an infrastructure to host static content (CV) on a S3 bucket.
Optional: 
•	Create a distribution (CloudFront, CDN) to distribute it worldwide with the minimal latency
•	Monitor resources through Amazon CloudWatch

## References
* [Configuring a static website on Amazon S3][ https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonS3/latest/userguide/HostingWebsiteOnS3Setup.html]
